tachyon.master

Class MasterClient

  • java.lang.Object
    • tachyon.master.MasterClient
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Closeable, AutoCloseable

    public final class MasterClient
extends Object
implements Closeable
    The client side of master server. Since MasterService.Client is not thread safe, this class is a wrapper of MasterService.Client to provide thread safety.
